suschad - Static UserSpace CHAnge Daemon. Watches your stuff, runs commands.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

0. DEPENDENCIES

Nothing. Just libstdc++ or whatever implementation you presumably already have
unless you've got so hyperbased that you don't have it. You likely do. Don't lie
to me.

. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .

1. BUILDING

Just run `make`.

. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .

2. CONFIGURATION

Consult `config/events.def` for example. The whole configuration DSL is
described in `include/dsl.hh`.

================================================================================
